{"tid":759361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登有愛]希望大家可以幫幫手認下樣捉小偷!!!!!1","createTime":"2018-07-28T14:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T03:43:42.000Z","uid":15311,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fd24c8fd64ee8c7accb8afbbb2d574e5c9115074","tid":759361,"uid":15311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">是咁的，上星期 22號，朝早9點幾，係太子既一間鋪到買野，我親戚因為個孫滿月，一大早就拎左錢滿心歡喜去買賀禮，到俾錢既時候，自己唔留神，掛住收其他親人打嚟既祝賀電話，咁就放低左個銀包，之後一直無人去拎，直到片中藍色衫個大姐發現，用兩包餅遮住我親戚個銀包咁就拎走左。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">之後我親戚去左報警，但警察既能力有幾多大家都清楚，除左捉呀婆掉垃圾勁之外，就係拉鳩反政府既人，幫小市民就無能唯力，親戚自己唔見銀包就由好開心賀孫仔滿月變到勁唔開心，因為銀包係屋企人送既禮物，入面有極大量開工要用既證件，信用卡，同用嚟買回禮俾人既錢‧ 作為親戚，真係睇唔過眼，佢咁傷心，所以第一次開post希望巴絲打們幫幫手，人間有愛。</span><br />\n<br />\n條cctv片係到 希望大家幫手睇下認下，雖然濛濛地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tr44eOsjUoE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftr44eOsjUoE&d=lSILiO91gCnBUF%2B6whAwRL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d5c4657c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tr44eOsjUoE</a>"},{"pid":"72e728d4b185f69b8554944b23d2db58c171ffef","tid":759361,"uid":15311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c24b0e6783e38523ae2c77c46e5d90060eaa404","tid":759361,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e667ec944116a49196506380e3f1152de3fc5801","tid":759361,"uid":18276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a3f3de3d459b1f405e70a541da3dabcca58b4fcf","tid":759361,"uid":11336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"幫下你推"},{"pid":"2339af1cea880811e66d2b7d01506db5902fa41d","tid":759361,"uid":15311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"謝巴絲們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/